Note on source documents:

The records in this corpus point at IETF RFCs and Internet-Drafts
hosted by the IETF Trust on rfc-editor.org and datatracker.ietf.org.
The source documents themselves are copyrighted by their authors and
distributed under the IETF Trust Legal Provisions
(https://trustee.ietf.org/license-info/). This corpus does not
redistribute source-document content.

If/when LLM-extracted elements are added to corpus/elements/, those
records will carry their own license header (CC-BY-4.0 with
attribution to the originating RFC or draft section).
